 Kho-ni2 kong2, khah siong5 si7 poaN3 jit8 eng5, chong2-si7 sim2-mih8 lang5 beh chhiaN3 goa2 chit e5 gin2-na2 choe3 kang? Lek8-tek-kou kong2, Goa2 u7 chu2-i3, lin2 toa3 teh che7, thiaN goa2 kong2. Goa2 chiu7 kin2 ai3 thiaN i chu2-i3 chaiN2-iuN7. Lek8-tek-kou kong2, Li2 bat Au7-bun5 mah? i ia7 si7 kap lin2 ti7 hai2-piN khia7, si7 pai2-kha e5. Kho-ni2 thiaN liau2 thim3 thau5. Lek8-tek-kou koh kong2, Au7-bun5 si7 goa2 e5 goa7 sun, si7 chin ho2 e5 gin2-a2, ia7 kap goa2 chin chhin-jiat8. Teng2 le2-pai3 lai5 chia ka7 goa2 kong2, Hit-e5 ia2-chhai3 chin7 ho2, liam5-piN oe7 sek8, chi2 kui2 ni5 long2 bo5 chhin-chhiuN7 kin-ni5 chiah toa7 chang5, koh am7; goa2 na7 si7 bo5 pai2-kha, chiu7 khi3 khau thang than3 chiN5 hou7 pe7-bu2, in-ui7 chit tiap8 lau7-pe7 phoa3-piN7 long2 bo5 chek-thiok, beh siuN7-khoaN3 u7 hoat-tou7 thang lai5 pou2-thiap. 
 Cha2 goa2 kap Kho-ni2 sui-jian5 chai soaN-piN, hai2-chui2 im-tioh8 hit-e5 chioh8 phang7, chiu7 siN-chhut hit e5 ia2-chhai3, u7 lang5 eng7 chhou3 chim3 choe3 chhai3, khiok bo5 siuN7 kau3 khau lai5 thang boe7. Koh thiaN-kiN3 Lek8-tek-kou kong2, Goa2 in-ui7 Au7-bun5 kong2 che oe7, chiu7 siuN7 Kho-ni2 thang kap i saN-kap khi3. Au7-bun5 in u7 chit8 chiah lu5, ia7 u7 chit8 tiuN chhia, li2 khi3 ka7 in lau7-pe7 chioh, i tek-khak beh chioh li2. Goa2 kah Au7-bun5 chhoa7 li2 khi3 chhut chhai3 e5 sou2-chai7, ka7 li2 kong2 tah-loh8 chit8 ui7 chhai3 toa7 chang5 khah ho2, li2 thang tah8 chioh8-thau5 chit8 chan5 chit8 chan5 peh kau3 koaiN5 e5 sou2-chai7 khi3 khau chhai3, theng3-hau7 chhia tiN7, chiah thoa-khi3 siaN5-lai7 boe7; sou2 boe7 e5 chiN5 lin2 piN5 pun, Kho-ni2 na7 pun chit8 poaN3 goa2 siuN7 chiu7 thang boe2 chit8 sin i-chiuN5. 
 Kho-ni2 thiaN liau2, chiu7 tah chhiu2 kong2, He2, an2-ni chin ho2, chhiaN2 li2 ka7 Au7-bun5 kong2, mng7 i beh siaN2 si5 khi3. Chiu7 siaN2 si5 khi3, hit e5 peh soaN poaN5 nia2 goa2 chin oe7, na7 m7 si7 li2 tiam2-chhiN2 goa2 chit-e5 hoat-tou7 than3 chiN5, goa2 long2 ia7 siuN7 bo5 kau3. Hit-e5 Lek8-tek-kou chiu7 koh kong2, Long2 si7 in-ui7 Au7-bun5 chit-e5 gin2-a2 kek8 ho2, m7 si7 an2-ni, chiu7 bo5 hou7 li2 kap i khi3, goa2 ia7 siuN7 i kap li2 choe3 tui, si7 hou7 goa2 an sim. 
 Lek8-tek-kou au7-lai5 kap Au7-bun5 kong2 beng5, koh kap goa2 iok tiaN7 jit8-chi2 khi3 khau chhai3. Kau3 hit jit8, goa2 kap Kho-ni2 chiu7 saN-kap khi3, khi2-thau5 i m7 hou7 goa2 khi3, goa2 kah i hou7 goa2 khi3, beh kap i tau3 pang-chan7, chiah hou7 goa2 khi3. Goan2 kau3 Au7-bun5 in tau, i chhia i2-keng tau3 ho2, long2 chhong3 chiau5-pi7. Che chhia pun2 si7 eng7 be2 thoa, eng7 lu5 lai5 thoa khah bo5 hap8-sek. Goa2 kap Kho-ni2 che7 ti7 chhia-teng2, Au7-bun5 chiu7 khia7 ti7 chhia-nih koaN2 chhia. Kho-ni2 ka7 goa2 pho7-teh, in-ui7 hia long2 si7 chhan5-nih e5 chhiN lou7, chin7 bo5 piN5. 
 Kho-ni2 mng7 Au7-bun5 kong2, Li2 phah-sng3 chiong chhia lai5 khoa3 ti7 hai2 piN teng2, a2-si7 thoa khi3 soaN-nih, khoa3 ti7 soaN-pho teng2, theng3-hau7 goa2 khau chhai3? I kong2, Khoa3 ti7 hai2-piN boe7 choe3-tit, chui2 the3 e5 si5, put-ko3 lou7-chhut kui2 chhioh soa-toe7, ia7 boe7 khoa3-tit chhia. Goa2 i2-keng siuN7 lah, chit tiap8 sou2 kiaN5 e5 lou7, chiu7 phah-sng3 chiong chhia thoa chiuN7 soaN khi3, khoa3 ti7 oe7 thoa-tit chhia e5 sou2-chai7; goa2 kap li2 tau3 theh8 soh-a2 kap kheng, kau3 kek8 koaiN5 e5 sou2-chai7, li2 chiah khi3 hi2 soaN-pou-nih khau chhai3, theng3-hau7 khau kau3 kheng moa2, goa2 kap Kui-lo5 eng7 soh-a2 tioh8 chiuN7-lai5, khi3 he7 chhia-nih, li2 chiah eng7 kheng koh khi3 khau, chi2 nng7 khia kheng oaN7-lai5 oaN7-khi3. Kho-ni2 kong2, He2, chin ho2-se3, lan2 chiu7 thang chai3-tit chit8 chhia chhai3. Chit e5 soaN si7 ti7 hai2-piN, kap chhut ian5-khong3 e5 soaN saN-lian5, ti7 hit-e5 sio2 soaN-teng2 u7 chit8 tiau5 lou7, Au7-bun5 siuN7 beh tui3 chit tiau5 lou7 chiong chhia thoa kau3 hai2-piN e5 soaN-teng2, bo5 phah-sng3 na2 kiaN5 lou7 na2 kham2-khiat8. Kho-ni2 chiu7 kap goa2 loh8 chhia. 
 Au7-bun5 kong2, Che chhia boe7 koh chin3 lah, tioh8 khoa3-he7 chia. Goan2 chiu7 sia3 chhia, pang3 lu5 khi3 chiah8 chhau2. Goan2 saN lang5 toa3 kheng kap soh-a2, un5-un5-a2 chin3-cheng5 khi3. Che lou7 sui-bong2 phaiN2-kiaN5, pi2 pe5 kau3 soaN-piN khi3 khau chhai3 khiok u7 khah koe7. Goan2 kau3 kek8 koaiN5 e5 sou2-chai7 Au7-bun5 m7 kaN2 pe5 loh8 soaN. Kho-ni2 chiu7 thng3 saN beh ka-ki7 loh8-khi3, goa2 chiu7 kah i hou7 goa2 kap i saN-kap loh8-khi3, kong2, Li2 chai goa2 kap li2 chit8 iuN7 oe7 peh soaN poaN5 nia2, long2 bo5 chit8 tiam2-a2 kiaN, na7 si7 lan2 nng7 lang5 loh8-khi3, tau3 kha-chhiu2, khau khah kin2. Koh sou2 khau e5 chhai3, than3 hai2-piN e5 chui2, soe2 thoa7 chheng-khi3 chiah ho2, na7 tiam3 teng2-bin7, chi7-chui7-a2 oe7 ka7 li2 soe2? Kho-ni2 kong2, Li2 beh kap goa2 loh8-khi3 ia7 oe7 choe3-tit; na7 sai2 theh8 soh-a2, kau3 hit e5 oe7 khia7-tit e5 sou2-chai7, chiu7 toa3 hia soe2 chhai3, hou7 goa2 ka-ki7 chit8 lang5 khi3 khau. 
 Goan2 tiam3 ti7 soaN-teng2 si3-ui5 khoaN3, chi2 kiN3 cheng5-bin7 u7 toa7 hai2, hai2 piN u7 choe7-choe7 tho2-hi5 chun5, khoaN3 khah hng7-nih, chui2-bin7 u7 chit8 chiah toa7 chun5; au7-bin7 u7 chan5-chan5 thah8-thah8 e5 soaN, u7 lek8-lek8 e5 chhiu7-na5, khoaN3-kiN3 ian-tang5 lai7 kek ian chhut-lai5, chhin-chhiuN7 ou hun5, cho2-iu7 u7 choe7-choe7 siaN5, kap hiuN-sia7, koh u7 choe7-choe7 beh8-hng5, thiaN-kiN3 hng7-hng7 u7 liam5-a2 kap chhiuN3 koa e5 siaN. Kau3 goan2 pe5 loh8 soaN kui2 pou7, chiu7 long2 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3, tui3 e7-toe2 chit8 e7 khoaN3, khoaN3-kiN3 ou kham5-kham5 e5 hai2-chui2, sou2 thiaN-kiN3 na7 u7 kek8 toa7 hai2-eng2 e5 siaN, chit sou2-chai7 leng2-cheng7, bo5 poaN3 lang5, sui si7 chheng-thian pek8-jit8, goa2 e5 sim iah8 kiaN. Kho-ni2 ti7 thau5-cheng5 kiaN5, goa2 kio3 i to3-tng2 lai5 hu5 goa2 loh8-khi3. Goan2 kau3 lou7 e5 poaN3 io, keng-ke3 chit8 e5 sio2 soaN-tong7, Kho-ni2 beh khia7-teh khoaN3 lai7-bin7, goa2 thiaN-kiN3 lai7-bin7 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 u7 thou2-khui3 e5 siaN, chiu7 khiN5 i, kah i kin2 chau2, i khoaN3 goa2 e5 bin7-sek, kiaN kau3 tng7 tih huih-sek, chiu7 chhio3 goa2 kong2, Kui-lo5, li2 phah-sng3 hi2 lai7-bin7 u7 sai mah? m7 sai2 kiaN, na7 u7, goa2 oe7 po2-hou7 li2. I an2-ni an-ui3 goa2, si7 beh kah goa2 m7 sai2 kiaN, ho2 thang choe3 goan2 e5 kang. 
 Kau3 hit e5 chhut chhai3 e5 sou2-chai7, Kho-ni2 ka7 goa2 chhe7 chit8 e5 piN5 chheng-khi3 e5 sou2-chai7, kah goa2 toa3 hia soe2 chhai3. I khau chhai3 long2 khoa3 ti7 goa2 e5 sin-piN, goa2 soe2 chheng-khi3 chiah khoa3 ti7 kheng-nih, na7 u7 hou7 Au7-bun5 thoa oe7 tin2-tang7 na7-tiaN7, goa2 chiu7 chhut ki3-ho7, kah i thoa chiuN7-khi3, i thoa e5 si5 chi2 kiN3 hit e5 kheng tit8-tit8 chiuN7-khi3. Au7-bun5 chit8 piN thoa goan2 chit8 piN koh he7, theng3-hau7 i lui7 khang kheng loh8-lai5, chiah koh chiong toe2 chhai3 e5 kheng hou7 i thoa chiuN7-khi3, goan2 eng7 nng7 khia kheng lai5 saN thoe3-oaN7. 
 Kau3 khau u7 choe7-choe7 kheng, Au7-bun5 tui3 teng2-bin7 chhut ki3-ho7, goan2 chiu7 chai toe2 tiN7-lah, m7 sai2 koh khau. Chit si5 thiN beh am3-lah, goan2 tioh8 un5-un5-a2 khi2 khi3, in-ui7 lou7 khoaN3 bo5 sim2-mih8 hian7, kau3 tu2-a2-chiah kiaN5 ke3 e5 soaN-tong7 Kho-ni2 kong2, Li2 toa3 chia theng3-hau7 bak8-nih-a2 ku2, goa2 beh khi3 lai7-bin7 ka7 i khoaN3-khoaN3 cheh, ian5-chhian5 ia7 m7 sai2 loa7 ku2. Goa2 kong2, Ku2 am3-lah, li2 kau3 lai7-bin7 ia7 boe7 khoaN3-kiN3 sim2-mih8. Goa2 chin m7 ai3 i jip8 khi3 hi2 lai7-bin7, koh m7 ai3 kong2-chhut, kou-put-chiong tiam3 ti7 goa7-bin7 teh theng3-hau7 i, i khi3 chit8 bak8-nih-a2 ku2, chiu7 thiaN-kiN3 u7 kha-pou7 siaN, khoaN3-kiN3 chit8 lang5 pi2 Kho-ni2 khah toa7-han3, tui3 soaN-tong7-nih chhut lai5, koaN2-kin2 chiuN7-khi3, goa2 chin kiaN, in-ui7 chit8 e7 khoaN3 chit lang5 na2 bin7-sek8 bin7-sek8, lai5 kau3 tui3 goa2 bin7-cheng5 ke3, siong5-se3 khoaN3 i e5 khoan2-sit, si7 Hou7-ni2. Kho-ni2 ia7 te3 au7-bin7 kin2 chhut-lai5, khia7 ti7 goa2 sin-piN, sui si7 jit8 am3 goa2 iau2-ku2 oe7 khoaN3-kiN3 i e5 bin7-sek u7 piN3, i chiu7 soe3-a2 siaN mng7 goa2 kong2, Kui-lo5, li2 u7 khoaN3-kiN3 mah? Goa2 kong2, U7 lah, tu2-a2 ke3-khi3, si7 Hou2-ni2. Kho-ni2 kong2, Bo5 chho3, i ti7 hi2 lai7-bin7, m7 chai choe3 sim2-mih8, i kiaN goa2 khoaN3-kiN3 u7 ng i e5 bin7, ke2 choe3 m7-bat goa2, kaN2 si7 i u7 choe3 sim2-mih8 put-hoat e5 tai7-chi3. 
 Goa2 kong2, Am3 lah; boh8-tit toa3 chia lan2 tioh8 lai5 khi3, ban7-ban7 chiah lai5 kong2 lah. Kho-ni2 chiu7 beng5-beng5 hoan-hu3 goa2 kong2, M7 sai2 ka7 Au7-bun5 kong2, ia7 boh8-tit ka7 lau7-bu2 kong2. 
 Te7 kau2 chiuN 
 Goan2 kiN3-tioh8 Au7-bun5 kap i su-niu5 beng5-pek8, kah i bin5-a2 cha2-khi2 jip8 siaN5 khi3 boe7 chhai3. Goa2 kap Kho-ni2 chiu7 saN-kap to3-khi3, na2 kiaN5 na2 kong2 goan2 kin-a2-jit8 oe7 khau chiah choe7 chhai3. Koh the5-khi2 tu2-a2-chiah Hou2-ni2 e5 su7. Kho-ni2 kong2, I khi3 hia, kaN2 ia7 bo5 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3, phah-sng3 si7 thit-tho5. Goa2 kong2, Na7 bo5 sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3, i siaN2-su7 kiaN, chiu7 choe3 i chau2? Kho-ni2 kong2, M7 chai i khoaN3-kiN3 si7 goa2 a2 m7 si7,hit si5 goa2 ia7 chin kiaN. Goa2 kong2, Li2 to3-khi3 beh ka7 lau7-bu2 kong2 mah? I kong2, U7 sim2-mih8 thang kong2? I na7 bo5 kong2, lan2 chiu7 m7 sai2 kong2; i na7 u7 kong2-khi2, lan2 chiah kong2, li2 m7 sai2 chiong chit e5 tai7-chi3 khoa3 sim. 
 Ke3 bin5-a2 cha2-khi3, Au7-bun5 chhai3 boe7-liau2, boe7 chin7 choe7 chiN5. Kho-ni2 chiu7 pun kui2 chheng chiN5, hiah-e5 chiN5 chha-put-to u7 kau3-giah8 i boe2 tit chit8 sin i-chiuN5. Lau7-bu2 chiu7 chin hoaN-hi2, in2 beh ka7 i boe2 pou3, soa3 ka7 i choe3 i-chiuN5. Koh kong2, Pai3-lak8 hiuN-chng u7 chu7-chip8, lin2 thang kap goa2 khi3 chian2-pou3. 
 Kau3 hit jit8 lak8 tiam2 cheng, goan2 chiu7 beh khi3, Hou2-ni2 iau2-be7 to3-lai5. Lau7-bu2 chiong choan7-si5 khoa3 ti7 tiaN7-tioh8 e5 sou2-chai7, khah koe7 chhe7, chiu7 saN-kap chhut-lai5. Goan2 chioh chit8 chiah lu5 hou7 Pi2-tek khia5, Kho-ni2 ka7 i khan, lau7-bu2 kap goa2 ti7 au7-bin7 te3 in kiaN5, goan2 long2 hoaN-hi2, in-ui7 m7-na7 beh ka7 Kho-ni2 boe2 pou3 choe3 i-chiuN7, lau7-bu2 ia7 beh boe2 oaN2-poaN5, kap ka-ki7 chheng7 e5 i-chiuN5, koh in2 beh ka7 goa2 boe2 ni5-soaN3 kah goa2 khi3 kiu5 Lek8-tek-kou ka3 goa2 chhiah beh8. Hiah-e5 teh chu7-chip8 e5, si7 ti7 hiuN-li2 tiong chit8 e5 khang3-toe7, chit jit8 si7 ti7 ian5-khong3 choe3 kang lang5 theh8 kang-chiN5 e5 jit8-chi2, in e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 choe7-choe7 chu7-chip8 khi3 boe2 mih8, sou2-i2 khi3 chu7-chip8 e5 lang5 choe7, ia7 u7 thang khoaN3 piN3 kau5-lang7. Goan2 tai7-seng bo5 khi3 khoaN3 hiah-e5, chiu7 khi3 boe7 hui5-khi3 e5 sou2-chai7, lau7-bu2 boe2 oaN2-phiat, koh ka7 Pi2-tek boe2 chit8 te3 te5-au, hit e5 te5-au u7 kim-ji7, chhau3-tu2-kham2 si7 i e5 mia5-ji7. Te7 it iau3-kin2 si7 beh chian2 pou3, bo5 siuN7 khi3 khoaN3 pat8 hang7, ti7 hia goan2 keng2 chit8 phit kek8 ho2 chin7 pui5 e5 pou3 si7 he-sek e5. Lau7-bu2 mng7 i e5 ke3-chiN5, si7 pi2 Koh-ni2 sou2 than3-e5 ke nng7 chheng chiN5. Kho-ni2 bo5 kong2 beh hit e5 pou3 ia7 bo5 kong2 poaN3 ku3 oe7, goa2 chiu7 beh koh khi3 pat8 ui7 khoaN3, goan2 lau7-bu2 chit8 e7 siuN7 kong2, che pou3 chap8 hun7 ho2, ia7 bo5 kui3, chiu7 thiN chiN5 ka7 i boe2. 
 Goa2 long2 bo5 kong2 sim2-mih8, i ka-ki7 ia7 bo5 boe2 poaN3 hang7, au7-lai5 chiah chai sou2 sin7 e5 chiN5 bo5 kau3 boe2 i sou2 chheng7 e5. Goa2 chiong pou3 pau ho2, chiu7 khi3 boe2 ni5 soaN3, boe2-liau2 goan2 chiah khi3 khoaN3 piN3 kau5-lang7. KhoaN3 ia3 lah, chiu7 siuN7 beh to3-khi3, goan2 tai7-ke chiu7 saN-kap to3-khi3; kiaN5 kau3 poaN3-lou7 Hou2-ni2 tui3 au7-bin7 koaN2 lai5, chiong i e5 chhiu2 moa ti7 Kho-ni2 e5 keng-thau5 un5-un5-a2 kiaN5, goa2 ti7 au7-bin7 te3 in, lau7-bu2 kap Pi2-tek ti7 thau5-cheng5. Hou2-ni2 kong2, Kho-ni2 li2 tioh8 choe3 ho2 lang5, bian2-tit hou7 goa2 kong2 peh8-chhat8, cha-bou7-jit8 li2 tu2-tioh8 goa2, m7 thang ka7 lau7-bu2 kong2. Kho-ni2 kong2, Li2 ti7 hi2 tong7-lai7 chhong3 sim2-mih8? I kong2, Li2 m7 sai2 koan2 goa2, beh ta2-loh8 khi3 si7 chhut-chai7 goa2, li2 thang khi3 hi2 chioh8 tong7-nih, goa2 chiu7 m7 thang khi3 mah? Li2 beh ka7 lau7-bu2 kong2, goa2 iau2-beh koh khah hou7 li2 ka7 lau7-bu2 kong2 nih. Hou2-ni2 chit8 piN kong2, chit8 piN chhio3. 
 Kho-ni2 kong2, Goa2 si7 khi3 khau chhai3, he li2 chai. Hou2-ni2 kong2, li2 thai2-tho2 chai goa2 m7 si7 khi3 khau chhai3 ah? Kho-ni2 kong2, Li2 na7 bo5 choe3 m7 tioh8 e5 su7, siaN2-su7 beh moa5 lau7-bu2? KhoaN3 li2 chit ho7 khoan2 sit8-chai7 boe7 pin5-sin3-tit, li2 ka7 goa2 kong2, tau3-ti2 si7-sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3? na7 bo5 beh chiu7 tioh8 kong2 hou7 lau7-bu2 chai; li2 na7 kong2, goa2 kap Kui-lo5 chiu7 bo5 the5-khi3. 
